OL,3,GLondon & South East
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FLargely
OL,6,Fclear with a slight frost, and perhaps
OL,7,Fpatchy fog, developing for some rural
OL,8,Flocations. Later areas of low cloud
OL,9,Fare likely to arrive, mainly across
OL,10,Feastern areas.
OL,11,
OL,12,CSunday:FEarly mist, patchy fog or low
OL,13,Fcloud will gradually disperse leaving
OL,14,Fbright conditions with high cloud.
OL,15,FBecoming warm inland again, except
OL,16,Fcooler across Kent and also for
OL,17,Fcoastal areas.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
